  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study evaluates the effect on gastro-oesophageal reflux (GOR) of infants sitting in a
      stable upright position during 20 min. This is an addendum to the previous study with record
      number clinical trials.gov NCT02124863
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
